  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213610/extras/b90a5f73b4b44166c6830fc10d76d900.avif?t=1766267674\" width=283 height=132 /></span><br><br>A shaman's ballard tells the story of Melody, a shaman apprentice summoned by the ancient goddess to go on a pilgrim journey for her shanar, the rite of initiation to the order of Aahkray. It turns out Erenblad holds more secrets than anticipated and Melody must use her sound bending abilities not only to reach the goddess, but also to protect the land from imminent danger.<br><br>Inspired by real shamanism. <br><br>FEATURES​<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a colorful and mysterious world<br></li><li>A pilgrim journey filled with danger<br></li><li>Strong focus on tactical combat, storytelling and aesthetics<br></li><li>Tactical turn-based RPG<br></li><li>Cute main characters in anime style</li></ul><br>CHARACTERS<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213610/extras/46da9b703e602516b98f26525a9ae60c.webp?t=1766267674\" width=36 height=48 /></span><br>Melody - shaman apprentice and sound bender<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213610/extras/42790aa0c10c078f5a429aa841e1781c.webp?t=1766267674\" width=37 height=47 /></span><br>Sacrista - wind archer<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213610/extras/fb6df6ab2807b75b631ef588a15d7ded.webp?t=1766267674\" width=39 height=46 /></span><br>Aju - shaman priest and shadow bender<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213610/extras/93ecff966710911f6230dc9de109d0b7.webp?t=1766267674\" width=31 height=48 /></span><br>Squalus - water/lightning arch mage",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213610/extras/b90a5f73b4b44166c6830fc10d76d900.avif?t=1766267674\" width=283 height=132 /></span><br><br>A shaman's ballard tells the story of Melody, a shaman apprentice summoned by the ancient goddess to go on a pilgrim journey for her shanar, the rite of initiation to the order of Aahkray. It turns out Erenblad holds more secrets than anticipated and Melody must use her sound bending abilities not only to reach the goddess, but also to protect the land from imminent danger.<br><br>Inspired by real shamanism. <br><br>FEATURES​<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a colorful and mysterious world<br></li><li>A pilgrim journey filled with danger<br></li><li>Strong focus on tactical combat, storytelling and aesthetics<br></li><li>Tactical turn-based RPG<br></li><li>Cute main characters in anime style</li></ul><br>CHARACTERS<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213610/extras/46da9b703e602516b98f26525a9ae60c.webp?t=1766267674\" width=36 height=48 /></span><br>Melody - shaman apprentice and sound bender<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213610/extras/42790aa0c10c078f5a429aa841e1781c.webp?t=1766267674\" width=37 height=47 /></span><br>Sacrista - wind archer<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213610/extras/fb6df6ab2807b75b631ef588a15d7ded.webp?t=1766267674\" width=39 height=46 /></span><br>Aju - shaman priest and shadow bender<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213610/extras/93ecff966710911f6230dc9de109d0b7.webp?t=1766267674\" width=31 height=48 /></span><br>Squalus - water/lightning arch mage",
